DESCRIPTION
============

The tagger is the Model 4 described in Table 2 of (Reddy and Sharoff 2011). 

License:
=======

The tagger is distributed under GNU GPL license. Feel free to use, modify, and redistribute the files as necessary. We only ask you to cite our work in your paper/work. Citation details are given below

